 widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">09.在月球上拍摄的月球车特写</p><p class="f_center" style="; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><a target="_blank" href="http://static.cnbetacdn.com/newsimg/2013/0724/91374625133.jpg" style="color: rgb(0, 51, 102); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; "><img src="http://static.cnbetacdn.com/newsimg/2013/0724/91374625133.jpg_w600.jpg" id="PicSrc" style="border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; "/></a></p><p style="; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">10.&nbsp;宇航员大卫•斯科特正在月球表面作业</p><p class="f_center" style="; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><a target="_blank" href="http://static.cnbetacdn.com/newsimg/2013/0724/101374625133.jpg" style="color: rgb(0, 51, 102); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; "><img src="http://static.cnbetacdn.com/newsimg/2013/0724/101374625133.jpg_w600.jpg" id="PicSrc" style="border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; "/></a></p><p style="; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">11.&nbsp;宇航员迈克尔•柯林斯拍摄尼尔•阿姆斯特朗和巴兹•奥尔德林乘坐的登月舱</p><p class="f_center" style="; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><a target="_blank" href="http://static.cnbetacdn.com/newsimg/2013/0724/111374625133.jpg" style="color: rgb(0, 51, 102); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; "><img src="http://static.cnbetacdn.com/newsimg/2013/0724/111374625133.jpg_w600.jpg" id="PicSrc" style="border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; "/></a></p><p style="; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">12.&nbsp;宇航员奥尔德林正在进行太阳风实验</p><p class="f_center" style="; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><a target="_blank" href="http://static.cnbetacdn.com/newsimg/2013/0724/121374625134.jpg" style="color: rgb(0, 51, 102); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; "><img src="http://static.cnbetacdn.com/newsimg/2013/0724/121374625134.jpg_w600.jpg" id="PicSrc" style="border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; "/></a></p><p style="; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">13.&nbsp;阿波罗11号登陆月球的历史性标记</p><p class="f_center" style="; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><a target="_blank" href="http://static.cnbetacdn.com/newsimg/2013/0724/131374625134.jpg" style="color: rgb(0, 51, 102); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; "><img src="http://static.cnbetacdn.com/newsimg/2013/0724/131374625134.jpg_w600.jpg" id="PicSrc" style="border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; "/></a></p><p style="; ; ; ; ; ; ; ; vertical-align: baseline; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">14.&nbsp;阿波罗17号的宇航员拍摄的蓝色地球</p><p><br/></p>', '2013-07-24 09:09:47', NULL, 8, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'admin', 1, 1, '', 'normal', 'normal', 'float');
